text: Then nothing happened for a while. Our vacation duration was coming to a close. Checked everything off the list, and then some. I finished the mystery novel, it was the bell-up. One moment regarding the Valentine mob bubbles gave us each a special phone if we ever needed to connect. So we did. We called Luzel. Voice mail. We decided against leaving a message. A few moments later my friends formed bust. Everything okay.
Ask Chappen. Yes, I'm my friend. Okay, we're gathering you up tonight, be ready. My friend and I hiding our excitement said, okay. Breathe into Chappen, Chow.
